cs.CV, cs.CR, cs.MM, cs.LG, cs.HC 

The paper deals with the problem of monitoring people entering and exiting camera forbidden areas using computer vision. This falls under the domain of computer vision (cs.CV) and also has security concerns (cs.CR). The paper also involves the use of machine learning techniques (cs.MM) and evaluation of the proposed model (cs.LG). Additionally, the paper addresses the issue of privacy in public places (cs.HC).
